title: Turkey Crude Oil Imports From Russia
description: Crude Oil Imports from Russia in Turkey decreased to 943 Thousand Tonnes in August from 1066 Thousand Tonnes in July of 2022. Crude Oil Imports from Russia in Turkey averaged 334.94 Thousand Tonnes from 2008 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 1355 Thousand Tonnes in November of 2019 and a record low of 0 Thousand Tonnes in August of 2010. This page includes a chart with historical data for Turkey Crude Oil Imports From Russia.
author: EUROSTAT
